Cell["\<\
The first two arguments represent the bounds of the range (minimum and \
maximum values), while the optional third and fourth arguments (by default \
equal to 1 and 0) regulate the upper and lower bounds of the steps \
(differences between successive elements).\
\>", "Notes",
 TaggingRules-><|
  "ChatNotebookSettings" -> <|
    "InheritanceTest" -> True, 
     "ServiceDefaultModel" -> <|
      "OpenAI" -> "chatgpt-4o-latest", "LLMKit" -> Automatic|>, 
