Cell[TextData[{
 "A natural application of AlgebraicRange is in the search for closed forms \
for floating point numbers, possibly in terms of arbitrary combinations of \
mathematical functions with algebraic arguments, through \
ResourceFunction[\"",
 ButtonBox["FindClosedForm",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://resources.wolframcloud.com/FunctionRepository/resources/\
FindClosedForm"], None},
  ButtonNote->
   "https://resources.wolframcloud.com/FunctionRepository/resources/\
FindClosedForm"],
 "\"]."
}], "Notes",
